Package: zeRefdisk
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), smartmontools, nvme-cli, hdparm, util-linux
Maintainer: ZerefDisk Project <zeRefdisk@localhost>
Homepage: https://github.com/yourname/zeRefdisk
Description: SSD Forensic & Revival Engine
 ZerefDisk adalah tools diagnostik SSD/NVMe berbasis forensik.
 Mendeteksi, mendiagnosis, dan mencoba recovery pada SSD yang bermasalah.
 .
 Fitur utama:
  - Deteksi otomatis semua SSD/NVMe/SATA/USB
  - Analisa SMART data mendalam
  - Kernel error analysis via dmesg
  - Ghost device detection
  - Automatic recovery attempt engine
  - History tersimpan di SQLite
 .
 Verdict: HEALTHY / WARNING / DYING / DEAD / GHOST
 "Even the dead deserve a verdict."
